{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_01","textHome":"我从第一次来神滨的时候就感觉有些……违和。@乍一看，好像和我们住的见泷原没什么区别，@但空气中的魔力波动，和见泷原的完全不同。@不早不晚，就是那个时候感觉到的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_18","textHome":"我最喜欢的魔法……应该是做红茶的魔法吧。@战斗结束之后，能够休息一下就好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_19","textHome":"感觉自己跨越了界限。我还能更强吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_20","textHome":"我看到了……在我心中广阔的景色……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_21","textHome":"虽然我在成为魔法少女的时候，@没心思考虑活下去以外的愿望。@但如果有机会的话，@我又会怎么做呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_22","textHome":"过去我一直都是一个人在战斗。@作为魔法少女的烦恼辛苦还有害怕，@没法和任何人坦白，一直独自一人……@但是，现在我有了同伴……@所以我能够坚持下去……这是毋庸置疑的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_23","textHome":"和同伴一起战斗的时候特别安心、幸福。@这是一个人战斗的时候所感受不到的。@有和自己心意相通的人存在，@真是一件非常幸运的事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_24","textHome":"果然。哼哼……我感觉到了和你的羁绊，@预感到你是不是快要来了。@果真如此实在是太好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_25","textHome":"适合早餐的红茶大概是英伦早餐茶吧。@水正好也烧开了，你要喝一杯吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_26","textHome":"天气不错的时候，在外面吃午餐也很舒服呢。@坐在公园的长椅上，吹着舒服的风的时候……@该喝什么茶比较好呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_27","textHome":"虽然还说不上是下午茶的时间……@在平静的日子里，@喝上一杯红茶也是相当不错的哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_03","textHome":"看起来是麻烦的对手呢……小心为上……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_28","textHome":"啊，已经这个时间了吗？@聊着聊着没想到时间过得这么快。@熬夜可是美容的天敌，早点睡吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_29","textHome":"一个人住的话，休息日一不留神就过去了呢。@好想过得充实一点啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_30","textHome":"关于魔法少女……也就是我自己……@还有着很多我不知道的事情。@我们到底是什么样的存在？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_31","textHome":"对了，我也有想尝试的战术，@这样的战斗也不坏呢。@只不过，我会拿出真本事去战斗的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_32","textHome":"对手的出招，我能读到什么程度呢……@总之，第一次接触很重要。@就从那里开始计算吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_33","textHome":"魔法通过积累修行就能有新的体会……@这是我的亲身感受。@只不过也需要花费相应的时间就是了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_34","textHome":"之前，我找到了一家非常棒的蛋糕店！@每个蛋糕看起来都又可爱又好吃！@下次一起去怎么样？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_35","textHome":"我喜欢草本茶。@放松的时候喝上一杯洋甘菊茶，@能让身心都舒缓下来……@啊……好像该添置一些了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":400}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_36","textHome":"一个人的力量是薄弱的，但许多人集中起来@就能变成一股强大的力量……@这正是我用枪来战斗的方式。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_37","textHome":"说起来，虽然搭配红茶的甜品@交给了喜欢的蛋糕店来制作，@但平时的饭菜都是我自己做的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_04","textHome":"没问题……@我怎么会让可爱的后辈受伤呢……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_38","textHome":"除了味道……红茶的香气也让人十分喜欢呢。@你不觉得伯爵茶有着能让人放松的香味吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200500}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_39","textHome":"我喜欢洗澡的时候悠闲地泡在浴缸里。@抛开杂念，闭上眼